    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 46,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Zhongli_icon.png",
                      "name": "鍾離",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "選用黑纓槍作為鍾離武器，就意味著徹底放棄了輸出。因此，這柄武器僅適用於在聖遺物方面也全部選擇",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "生命值",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "的，完全追求",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "護盾",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "強度的玩家群體。而犧牲傷害所換取的，是幾乎無法被擊破的護盾。只要算好鍾離元素戰技的冷卻時間，可以達到偽無敵的效果，正所謂「堅如磐石」。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 16,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Thoma_icon.png",
                      "name": "托馬",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "托馬是一名以生命值上限為轉化基礎來提供護盾的角色。該武器提供的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "生命值",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "副詞條，同樣適合托馬使用。但托馬需要注意元素充能效率來保證元素爆發循環，以滿足不斷刷新護盾的需要，因此攜帶該武器時，時之沙位置需要根據實現的能量需求考慮是否應該攜帶元素充能效率。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2815,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/09/26/7998136/2f43da4ece9eabfbde6ec2fcc81b3bff_693228621905250476.png",
                      "name": "坎蒂絲",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器能夠提供高額的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "生命值",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "加成，可以提升坎蒂絲的傷害，且獲得難度低，可以作為過渡武器使用。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
